member.param:
The  that specifies a transformation to be applied to this path
            before the bounding rectangle is calculated. This path is not permanently transformed;
            the transformation is used only during the process of calculating the bounding rectangle.

member.summary:
Specifies that the format is 16 bits per pixel;
5 bits each are used for the red, green, and blue components.
The remaining bit is not used.

